## Government Tender Announcement

### Reference: WS4454135614

#### Project Summary

**Project Title: E6MON-24PQPR- P01 - RMSO Boxed Lunches**
**Publication Date: April 11, 2024**
**Tender Closing Date: May 7, 2024, at 14:00:00**

The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PWGSC) on behalf of the Department of National Defense invites qualified suppliers to respond to a Request for Standing Offer (RSO) for the supply of Boxed Lunches for government employees in Quebec, Canada.

### Tender Details

* **Contracting Entity**: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
* **Contracting Entity Address**: 11 Laurier St, Phase III, Place du Portage, Gatineau, QC, K1A 0S5, Canada
* **End-User Entities**: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)

* **Tender Status**: Expired (Please note: the tender is not available for response as it has closed).

* **Contract Period**: The contract will commence on an unspecified date and is anticipated to conclude by May 31, 2025.

* **Supply Spec**: Packaged combination meal (UNSPSC Code 50192700)

* **Procurement Category**: Government procurement (GD)

* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open bidding

* **Trade Agreements**: The procurement is open to contractors from the following trade agreements:
	+ Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
	+ Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
	+ Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
	+ Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
	+ World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
	+ Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
	+ Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
	+ Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)
	+ Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)
	+ Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
	+ Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
	+ Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)

### Contact Information

* **Contact Name**: Efoé Adjakly (SPAC/PSPC)
* **Contact Email**: efoe.adjakly@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
* **Contact Phone**:
